Kristin Bauer van Straten https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kristin_Bauer_van_Straten 0 Kristin Bauer van Straten (born November 26, 1966) is an American film and television actress, notable for her roles as vampire Pamela Swynford De Beaufort on the HBO television series True Blood, Jerry's girlfriend Gillian on Seinfeld, and as sorceress Maleficent in the ABC series Once Upon a Time.
